title: 13 and 14 of the Planning and Development and Foreshore (Amendment) Act
heading: 2. The 8th day of March 2023 is appointed as the day on which sections 3,
text_raw:
2. The 8th day of March 2023 is appointed as the day on which sections 3, 
13 and 14 of the Planning and Development and Foreshore (Amendment) Act 
2022 (No. 47 of 2022) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

7 March, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 10th March, 2023.
